---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About — Labi Joshua"
  description="I'm a product designer who loves figuring out how things work and how they are made."
>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="about-hero pt-16 pb-16 px-6 text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto">
    <span class="inline-block border border-dashed border-neutral-300 bg-neutral-100 rounded-full px-4 py-1 text-xs tracking-wide mb-6" style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);">
      This is me
    </span>
    <h1 class="font-serif text-5xl md:text-[52px] leading-[1.15] tracking-tight text-neutral-900">
      Welcome to <span style="color: #51782B;">my corner of the Interweb.</span>
    </h1>
  </section>

  <div class="about-content max-w-[1100px] mx-auto px-6">

    <!-- Intro: Photo + Bio -->
    <section class="intro-section mb-16">
      <div class="intro-photo">
        <img
          src="/images/about-profile.jpg"
          alt="Labi Joshua standing in an art gallery"
          class="w-full h-full object-cover object-top"
          loading="eager"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="intro-bio flex flex-col justify-center gap-4">
        <h2 class="font-serif leading-tight text-neutral-900" style="font-size: 40px;">
          <span style="color: #51782B;">Hi!</span> I'm Labi Joshua.
        </h2>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 text-sm text-neutral-500 leading-relaxed">
          <p>I am a product designer who loves figuring out how things work and how they are made.</p>
          <p>My journey started when I studied Industrial Design at FUTA. There, I learned to build and shape physical objects. In my second year, I discovered digital product design and started playing with how things look and now people use them. I realized that whether I am making a physical tool or a digital app, the same rule applies. The craft matters.</p>
          <p>Now, I spend most of my time focusing on the work behind the scenes. I am interested in finding better ways to get things done. I build systems and tools that make my work smooth and easy. My goal is to build systems that help me be more creative.</p>
          <p>Outside of work, you can find me watching a funny sitcom or looking at art. I am not a painter, but I have a lot of respect for the hard work and ideas that go into making art. I bring that same respect to my design work. I am always looking for ways to combine solid structure with creative ideas.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Stats -->
    <section class="stats-section mb-16">
      <div class="stat-card">
        <span class="stat-label">Based in:</span>
        <span class="stat-value">Lagos, Nigeria</span>
        <span class="stat-sub">UTC+1, Always available.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card">
        <span class="stat-label">Doing this for:</span>
        <span class="stat-value">3+ years</span>
        <span class="stat-sub">A lifetime of making things with my hands.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card">
        <span class="stat-label">Off the clock:</span>
        <span class="stat-value">Creative Consumer</span>
        <span class="stat-sub">Obsessed with sitcoms and art history.</span>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Gallery -->
    <section class="gallery-section" style="margin-bottom: 48px;">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-5">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-neutral-600">
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
            <line x1="2" y1="12" x2="22" y2="12"/>
            <path d="M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4-10z"/>
          </svg>
          Welcome to my world
        </div>
        <span class="text-sm text-neutral-400">Gallery</span>
      </div>

      <div class="gallery-grid">
        <div class="gallery-large bg-neutral-200">
          <img src="/images/gallery-desk.jpg" alt="Labi Joshua at his workspace" class="w-full h-full object-cover" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="gallery-mid bg-neutral-300">
          <img src="/images/gallery-cap.jpg" alt="Labi Joshua" class="w-full h-full object-cover" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="gallery-sm bg-neutral-200">
          <img src="/images/gallery-street.jpg" alt="" class="w-full h-full object-cover" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="gallery-sm bg-neutral-300">
          <img src="/images/gallery-friends.jpg" alt="" class="w-full h-full object-cover" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Me outside of work -->
    <section class="outside-section" style="margin-bottom: 48px;">
      <h2 class="outside-heading font-serif text-neutral-900">Me outside of work</h2>
      <div class="outside-content">
        <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 leading-relaxed" style="margin-bottom: 24px;">
          I keep my downtime creative. You will likely find me getting inspired by shows like Abstract, or tuning into Sticky Notes and The Futur to keep my design mind sharp.
        </p>
        <div class="outside-thumbnails">
          <div class="outside-thumb bg-blue-700">
            <img src="/images/thefutur.jpg" alt="The Futur" class="w-full h-full object-cover" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <div class="outside-thumb bg-red-500">
            <img src="/images/stickynotes.jpg" alt="Sticky Notes" class="w-full h-full object-cover" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- How I work -->
    <section class="two-col-section" style="margin-bottom: 48px;">
      <h2 class="two-col-heading font-serif text-neutral-900">How I work</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 leading-relaxed">
        I start by finding the real problem so I can build the best solution. I focus on making systems that are simple and built to last. I always try to improve my work and tools to make things run smoothly. Finally, I stay curious by looking at art and stories to find new ideas for my projects.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- Say hi -->
    <section class="two-col-section" style="margin-bottom: 48px;">
      <h2 class="two-col-heading font-serif text-neutral-900">Say hi.</h2>
      <div>
        <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 leading-relaxed" style="margin-bottom: 24px;">
          I'm currently taking on one new project for Q3 2026 — and always happy to swap notes on systems, tokens, or what to lift on a Tuesday. The fastest way is email.
        </p>
        <div class="contact-cards">
          <a href="mailto:jospecial34@gmail.com" class="contact-card">
            <span class="contact-label">Email</span>
            <span class="contact-value">jospecial34@gmail.com</span>
          </a>
          <div class="contact-card">
            <span class="contact-label">Phone number</span>
            <span class="contact-value">+234 816 9203 595</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </div>

</Layout>

<style>
  .about-hero {
    margin-bottom: 64px;
  }
  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .about-hero {
      display: none;
    }
    .about-content {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      padding-top: 48px;
    }
    .intro-section   { order: 1; }
    .gallery-section { order: 2; }
    .stats-section   { order: 3; }
    .outside-section { order: 4; }
    .about-content > section:nth-child(5) { order: 5; }
    .about-content > section:nth-child(6) { order: 6; }
  }

  .contact-cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 12px;
  }
  .contact-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 4px;
    background-color: #F9FAFB;
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 12px 20px;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .contact-label {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: #A3A3A3;
  }
  .contact-value {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-family: 'Instrument Serif', Georgia, serif;
    color: #51782B;
  }

  .two-col-section {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 40px;
    align-items: start;
  }
  .two-col-heading {
    font-size: 44px;
    line-height: 1.15;
  }
  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .two-col-section { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .two-col-heading { font-size: 36px; }
  }

  .outside-section {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 40px;
    align-items: start;
  }
  .outside-heading {
    font-size: 44px;
    line-height: 1.15;
  }
  .outside-thumbnails {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 16px;
  }
  .outside-thumb {
    border-radius: 16px;
    overflow: hidden;
    aspect-ratio: 1 / 1;
  }
  .outside-thumb img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }
  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .outside-section { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .outside-heading { font-size: 36px; }
  }

  .gallery-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 2fr 1.3fr 1fr;
    grid-template-rows: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 12px;
    height: 420px;
  }
  .gallery-large {
    grid-row: 1 / 3;
    border-radius: 16px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .gallery-mid {
    grid-row: 1 / 3;
    border-radius: 16px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .gallery-sm {
    border-radius: 16px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .gallery-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
      grid-template-rows: 1fr 1fr;
      height: 280px;
    }
    .gallery-mid { display: none; }
  }

  .stats-section {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 16px;
  }
  .stat-card {
    background-color: #F9FAFB;
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 24px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 6px;
  }
  .stat-label {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #A3A3A3;
  }
  .stat-value {
    font-family: 'Instrument Serif', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 24px;
    color: #51782B;
  }
  .stat-sub {
    display: block;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #A3A3A3;
    margin-top: 16px;
    text-align: right;
  }
  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .stats-section {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  .intro-section {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 40px;
    align-items: stretch;
  }
  .intro-photo {
    border-radius: 24px;
    overflow: hidden;
    background-color: #e5e5e5;
    width: 448px;
    height: 520px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .intro-photo img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: top;
    display: block;
  }
  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .intro-section {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .intro-photo {
      display: none;
    }
  }
</style>

